      public ChemicalElement(byte atomicNumber, String symbol, Map<String,String> names, double atomicWeight, double electronegativity, String electronConfig, int meltingPoint, int boilingPoint, byte[] oxidationNums, double standardElectrodePotential, Map<String,String> group)
      Constructor for ChemicalElement. Initializes the properties of the chemical element.
      Parameter:
      atomicNumber - Atomic number of the element.
      symbol - Symbol of the element.
      names - Map containing names of the element in different languages.
      atomicWeight - Atomic weight of the element.
      electronegativity - Electronegativity value of the element.
      electronConfig - Electron configuration string of the element.
      meltingPoint - Melting point in Kelvin.
      boilingPoint - Boiling point in Kelvin.
      oxidationNums - Array of oxidation numbers for the element.
      standardElectrodePotential - Standard electrode potential in volts.
      group - Map containing group information of the element.
